crypto: hisilicon - select NEED_SG_DMA_LENGTH in qm Kconfig

To avoid compile error in some platforms, select NEED_SG_DMA_LENGTH in
qm Kconfig.

Fixes: dfed0098ab91 ("crypto: hisilicon - add hardware SGL support")
